Create a function that takes an array of numbers as input and returns the average value.

CODE:
<?php
function calculateAverage($numbers) {
    if (count($numbers) === 0) {
        return 0; // Avoid division by zero
    }
    $sum = array_sum($numbers);   // Add all elements
    $count = count($numbers);     // Get number of elements
    return $sum / $count;         // Return average
}

// Example usage
$nums = [10, 20, 30, 40, 50];
echo "Average: " . calculateAverage($nums); 
?>

OUTPUT:
Average: 30
